    <div class="body">
        <p>If string begin at Russian "Р" ("Рп", "Рз" ...)and another character it return null.</p>

<p>$filter = new \Zend\Filter\StringTrim();
require_once 'Zend/Filter/StringTrim.php';
$filter2 = new \Zend_Filter_StringTrim();
$value = 'Расчет ';
var_dump($filter-&gt;filter($value));
var_dump($filter2-&gt;filter($value));</p>

<p>Result:
null
string 'Расчет' (length=12)</p>

<p>Expected result:
string 'Расчет' (length=12)
string 'Расчет' (length=12)</p>

